channel.title: Krysis-rs
channel.description:
~Krysis-rs, a Revolution in rsps's!~
We have
-Custom home -Dwarven City Building -The home tele is upstairs -The shops are downstairs -Theiving stalls -Makup mage -Duradel (slayer) -Zammorak Mage (runecrafting) -Wise old man (skillcapes shop)
-11 Different bosses -Corpreal beast, -Tormented Demons -God wars dungeon -Daggonoth kings -Nomad -Balanced Elemental -Skeletal Horror -King Black Dragon -3 Dungeoneering bosses, which are featured in our dungeoneering boss minigame. -Har'lak the Riftsplitter -Bal'lak the pummeler -To'kash the blood-chiller
-A lot of minigames -Fight cave -Barrows -Pest Control -Duel Arena -Fully working stake -Fully work options -Warriors Guild -Maze minigame (custom)
-Working skillcapes/skills -Attack -Strength -Defence -Magic -Ranging -Prayer -Magic -Runecrafting -Constituion -Agility -Herbivore -Theiving -Crafting -Slayer -Mining -Smithing -Fishing -Cooking -Firemaking -Woodcutting -Farming -Hunter -Quest Cape -Completionist Cape
-100% Working PKing! -Working wildy levels -Autocast -Working ancient warrior gear -Chaotics -Dragon claws -Hybriding -Curses -PK Points! -Can buy various items such as -Chaotics -Ancient warrior gear -Overloads -And alot of other cool things.
Now, here is a big thing I am working on.
-Prestiging system -Get all 99's and you can prestige. -Prestiges can yell, as well buy things at the prestige shop. -3 Prestige Tokens per prestige -Prestige shop includes alot of rares, such as -Completionist cape (15) -Korasi (5) -Primal (2 per peace) -Gilded (1 per peice) -I might add more soon.
